Original code is by Jan Vernier (Yann Vernier).
Simple utility for creation shared dictionaries (Djbz) in the DjVu files
Do only unifies equal shapes prom pages (in ex. letters).

Taken form:
    http://donkey.dyndns.org/~yann/jb2unify.cpp
See the big dialogue at the DjVuLibre forum about this program:
    http://sourceforge.net/forum/forum.php?thread_id=854907&forum_id=103286

Copy Makefile.in and jb2unify.cpp into tools,
replacing the old Makefile.in (works with DjVuLibre 3.5.14).
Restart configure and make.
